#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag16.6:4.1"
msgid "16.6. Selattheragāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:5.1"
msgid "<span class=\"cross\" title=\"^mn92#16 [Selasutta] | ^snp3.7#637 [Selasutta]\" id=\"note379\">*</span> <a class=\"verse-num-sc\" id=\"verse-num-sc818\"></a><a class=\"verse-num-pts\" id=\"verse-num-pts818\"></a>“Paripuṇṇakāyo suruci,"
msgstr "“Your body is perfect, you are radiant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:5.2"
msgid "Sujāto cārudassano;"
msgstr "Handsome, lovely to behold,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:5.3"
msgid "Suvaṇṇavaṇṇosi bhagavā,"
msgstr "Blessed One, you are golden coloured,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:5.4"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"susukkadāṭho virīyavā (bj) | susukkadāṭhosi viriyavā (s2, s3, pts1-2)\" id=\"note380\">Susukkadāṭhosi vīriyavā</span>."
msgstr "Your teeth are pure white, you are full of energy."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc819"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts819"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:6.1"
msgid "Narassa hi sujātassa,"
msgstr "The characteristics"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:6.2"
msgid "ye bhavanti viyañjanā;"
msgstr "Of a handsome man,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:6.3"
msgid "Sabbe te tava kāyasmiṃ,"
msgstr "The marks of a great man,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:6.4"
msgid "mahāpurisalakkhaṇā."
msgstr "Are all in your body."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:7.1"
msgid "<span class=\"cross\" title=\"^mn92#16 [Selasutta] | ^snp3.7#639 [Selasutta] | ^pe2#118 [Sāsanapaṭṭhānadutiyabhūmi]\" id=\"note381\">*</span> <a class=\"verse-num-sc\" id=\"verse-num-sc820\"></a><a class=\"verse-num-pts\" id=\"verse-num-pts820\"></a>Pasannanetto sumukho,"
msgstr "Your eyes are clear, your face is nice,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:7.2"
msgid "brahā uju patāpavā;"
msgstr "You are large, upright, and majestic."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:7.3"
msgid "Majjhe samaṇasaṃghassa,"
msgstr "In the middle of the Saṅgha of ascetics,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:7.4"
msgid "ādiccova virocasi."
msgstr "You shine like the sun."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc821"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts821"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:8.1"
msgid "Kalyāṇadassano bhikkhu,"
msgstr "You’re a good-looking monk,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:8.2"
msgid "kañcanasannibhattaco;"
msgstr "With skin like gold;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:8.3"
msgid "Kiṃ te samaṇabhāvena,"
msgstr "With such excellent appearance,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:8.4"
msgid "evaṃ uttamavaṇṇino."
msgstr "What do you want with the ascetic life?"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc822"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts822"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:9.1"
msgid "Rājā arahasi bhavituṃ,"
msgstr "You’re worthy of being a king,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:9.2"
msgid "cakkavattī rathesabho;"
msgstr "A wheel-rolling emperor, a lord of charioteers,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:9.3"
msgid "Cāturanto vijitāvī,"
msgstr "Victorious in the four directions,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:9.4"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"jambumaṇḍassa (mr)\" id=\"note382\">jambusaṇḍassa</span> issaro."
msgstr "Lord of all India."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc823"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts823"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:10.1"
msgid "Khattiyā <span class=\"var\" title=\"bhogā rājāno (bj, mr) | bhojarājāno (s2, s3, pts1-2)\" id=\"note383\">bhogī rājāno</span>,"
msgstr "Aristocrats, lords, and kings"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:10.2"
msgid "anuyantā bhavanti te;"
msgstr "Are your followers"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:10.3"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"rājādhirājā (bj, mr)\" id=\"note384\">Rājābhirājā</span> manujindo,"
msgstr "You are king above kings and lord of men—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:10.4"
msgid "rajjaṃ kārehi gotama”."
msgstr "Claim your kingship, Gotama!”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc824"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts824"></a><a class="pts" id="pts79"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:11.1"
msgid "“Rājāhamasmi sela,<span class=\"gathaQuote\">(selāti bhagavā)</span>"
msgstr "“Sela, I am a king,” said the Blessed One to Sela,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:11.2"
msgid "Dhammarājā anuttaro;"
msgstr "“The unsurpassed king of Dhamma."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:11.3"
msgid "Dhammena cakkaṃ vattemi,"
msgstr "By Dhamma I set the wheel rolling,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:11.4"
msgid "Cakkaṃ appaṭivattiyaṃ”."
msgstr "The wheel which cannot be rolled back.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc825"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts825"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:12.1"
msgid "“Sambuddho paṭijānāsi,<span class=\"gathaQuote\">(iti selo brāhmaṇo)</span>"
msgstr "“You claim to be awakened,” said Sela the brahman,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:12.2"
msgid "Dhammarājā anuttaro;"
msgstr "“The unsurpassed king of Dhamma. "

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:12.3"
msgid "‘Dhammena cakkaṃ vattemi’,"
msgstr "‘By Dhamma I set the wheel rolling’,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:12.4"
msgid "Iti bhāsatha gotama."
msgstr "That is what you say, Gotama."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc826"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts826"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:13.1"
msgid "Ko nu senāpati bhoto,"
msgstr "Who is the Blessed One’s general,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:13.2"
msgid "sāvako <span class=\"var\" title=\"satthu anvayo (bj)\" id=\"note385\">satthuranvayo</span>;"
msgstr "The disciple who follows the teacher?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:13.3"
msgid "Ko <span class=\"var\" title=\"te maṃ anuvatteti (bj) | imaṃ anuvatteti (pts1) | t'etaṃ anuvatteti (pts2)\" id=\"note386\">tetamanuvatteti</span>,"
msgstr "Who keeps on rolling"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:13.4"
msgid "dhammacakkaṃ pavattitaṃ”."
msgstr "The wheel of Dhama you rolled forth?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc827"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts827"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:14.1"
msgid "“Mayā pavattitaṃ cakkaṃ,<span class=\"gathaQuote\">(selāti bhagavā)</span>"
msgstr "“I rolled forth the wheel,” said the Blessed One to Sela,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:14.2"
msgid "Dhammacakkaṃ anuttaraṃ;"
msgstr "“The unexcelled wheel of Dhamma."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:14.3"
msgid "Sāriputto anuvatteti,"
msgstr "Sāriputta, who follows the Tathāgata’s example,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:14.4"
msgid "Anujāto tathāgataṃ."
msgstr "Keeps it rolling on."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc828"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts828"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:15.1"
msgid "Abhiññeyyaṃ abhiññātaṃ,"
msgstr "What’s to be known is known;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:15.2"
msgid "bhāvetabbañca bhāvitaṃ;"
msgstr "What’s to be developed is developed;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:15.3"
msgid "Pahātabbaṃ pahīnaṃ me,"
msgstr "I’ve abandoned what’s to be abandoned;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:15.4"
msgid "tasmā buddhosmi brāhmaṇa."
msgstr "Therefore, brahmin, I am a Buddha."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc829"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts829"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:16.1"
msgid "Vinayassu mayi kaṅkhaṃ,"
msgstr "Dispel your doubt in me;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:16.2"
msgid "adhimuccassu brāhmaṇa;"
msgstr "Make up your mind, brahman!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:16.3"
msgid "Dullabhaṃ dassanaṃ hoti,"
msgstr "It’s always hard to gain"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:16.4"
msgid "sambuddhānaṃ abhiṇhaso."
msgstr "The sight of Buddhas."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc830"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts830"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:17.1"
msgid "Yesaṃ ve dullabho loke,"
msgstr "I am one of those whose appearance"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:17.2"
msgid "pātubhāvo abhiṇhaso;"
msgstr "Is always hard to find in this world;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:17.3"
msgid "Sohaṃ brāhmaṇa buddhosmi,"
msgstr "I am a Buddha, brahman,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:17.4"
msgid "sallakatto anuttaro."
msgstr "The supreme surgeon."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc831"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts831"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:18.1"
msgid "Brahmabhūto atitulo,"
msgstr "Holy, unequalled,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:18.2"
msgid "mārasenappamaddano;"
msgstr "Crusher of Māra’s army;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:18.3"
msgid "Sabbāmitte <span class=\"var\" title=\"vasī (s2, s3, pts1-2, mr ^mn92#16 [Selasutta]; ^snp4.16#875 [Sāriputtasutta])\" id=\"note387\">vase</span> katvā,"
msgstr "Having subdued all enemies,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:18.4"
msgid "modāmi akutobhayo”."
msgstr "I rejoice, fearing nothing in any direction.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc832"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts832"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:19.1"
msgid "“Idaṃ bhonto nisāmetha,"
msgstr "“Listen, sirs, to what,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:19.2"
msgid "yathā bhāsati cakkhumā;"
msgstr "Is spoken by the seer."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:19.3"
msgid "Sallakatto mahāvīro,"
msgstr "surgeon, great hero,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:19.4"
msgid "sīhova nadatī vane."
msgstr "Roaring like a lion in the jungle."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc833"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts833"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:20.1"
msgid "Brahmabhūtaṃ atitulaṃ,"
msgstr "Holy, unequalled,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:20.2"
msgid "mārasenappamaddanaṃ;"
msgstr "Crusher of Māra’s army;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:20.3"
msgid "Ko disvā nappasīdeyya,"
msgstr "Who could see him and not have faith,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:20.4"
msgid "api kaṇhābhijātiko."
msgstr "Even one whose nature is dark?"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc834"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts834"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:21.1"
msgid "Yo maṃ icchati anvetu,"
msgstr "Those who wish may follow me;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:21.2"
msgid "yo vā nicchati gacchatu;"
msgstr "Those who don’t wish may go."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:21.3"
msgid "Idhāhaṃ pabbajissāmi,"
msgstr "Right here, I’ll go forth,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:21.4"
msgid "varapaññassa santike”."
msgstr "In the presence of this man of splendid wisdom.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="18"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc835"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts835"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:22.1"
msgid "“Etañce ruccati bhoto,"
msgstr "“If, sir, you approve"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:22.2"
msgid "sammāsambuddhasāsanaṃ;"
msgstr "The teaching of the Buddha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:22.3"
msgid "Mayampi pabbajissāma,"
msgstr "We will also go forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:22.4"
msgid "varapaññassa santike”."
msgstr "In the presence of this man of splendid wisdom.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="19"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc836"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts836"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:23.1"
msgid "“Brāhmaṇā tisatā ime,"
msgstr "These three hundred brahmans"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:23.2"
msgid "yācanti pañjalīkatā;"
msgstr "With hands held in añjalī, ask:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:23.3"
msgid "‘Brahmacariyaṃ carissāma,"
msgstr "“May we live the holy life"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:23.4"
msgid "bhagavā tava santike’”."
msgstr "In your presence, Blessed One?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="20"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc837"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts837"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:24.1"
msgid "“Svākkhātaṃ brahmacariyaṃ,<span class=\"gathaQuote\">(selāti bhagavā)</span>"
msgstr "“The holy life is well proclaimed,” said the Buddha to Sela,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:24.2"
msgid "Sandiṭṭhikamakālikaṃ;"
msgstr "“Apparent in this very life, without delay,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:24.3"
msgid "Yattha amoghā pabbajjā,"
msgstr "In which the going forth isn’t in vain,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:24.4"
msgid "Appamattassa sikkhato”."
msgstr "For one heedful in the training.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="21"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc838"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts838"></a><a class="pts" id="pts80"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:25.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ taṃ <span class=\"var\" title=\"saraṇamāgamma (bj, s2, s3, pts1)\" id=\"note388\">saraṇamāgamha</span>,"
msgstr "“It’s the eighth day, o seer,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:25.2"
msgid "ito <span class=\"var\" title=\"aṭṭhami (s2, s3, pts1-2, mr)\" id=\"note389\">aṭṭhame</span> cakkhuma;"
msgstr "Since we went to you for refuge."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:25.3"
msgid "Sattarattena bhagavā,"
msgstr "In seven days, Blessed One,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:25.4"
msgid "dantāmha tava sāsane."
msgstr "We were tamed in your teaching."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="22"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc839"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts839"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:26.1"
msgid "Tuvaṃ buddho tuvaṃ satthā,"
msgstr "You are the Buddha, you are the teacher"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:26.2"
msgid "tuvaṃ mārābhibhū muni;"
msgstr "You are the sage who has overcome Māra;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:26.3"
msgid "Tuvaṃ anusaye chetvā,"
msgstr "You have cut off the tendencies,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:26.4"
msgid "tiṇṇo tāresimaṃ pajaṃ."
msgstr "And having crossed over yourself, you bring people across."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="23"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc840"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts840"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:27.1"
msgid "Upadhī te samatikkantā,"
msgstr "You have transcended attachments,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:27.2"
msgid "āsavā te padālitā;"
msgstr "Your defilements have been torn apart;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:27.3"
msgid "Sīhova anupādāno,"
msgstr "Without grasping, like a lion,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:27.4"
msgid "pahīnabhayabheravo."
msgstr "You’ve abandoned fear and dread."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="24"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc841"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts841"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.6:28.1"
msgid "Bhikkhavo tisatā ime,"
msgstr "These three hundred monks"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:28.2"
msgid "tiṭṭhanti pañjalīkatā;"
msgstr "Stand with hands in añjalī:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:28.3"
msgid "Pāde vīra pasārehi,"
msgstr "Put out your feet, great hero,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.6:28.4"
msgid "nāgā vandantu satthuno”ti."
msgstr "Let these beings of power venerate the teacher.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag16.6:29.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thag16.6:29.2"
msgid "Selo thero …."
msgstr ""
